ss.udapi.sdk

Class ResourceImpl

  • java.lang.Object
    • ss.udapi.sdk.ResourceImpl
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Resource

    public class ResourceImpl
extends java.lang.Object
implements Resource
    An object of this class represents an instance of a resource a.k.a fixture. It provides a means of controlling monitoring of an active resource for the client system(s).
